data.description: HUGE SAVINGS with 2-1 Rate Buydown (with an acceptable offer & Sellers preferred lender) and 1 Year Home Warranty ($775 value).  Beautiful all brick 4bd, 3ba home is move-in ready and just waiting for you. Located on a quiet cul-de-sac, this 1.75 acre property makes you feel like you’re in your own private oasis. Relax on your oversized 30’ back deck or soak in nature from your Gazebo. Or have S’mores over the fire pit. Beautiful landscaping and mature trees all around (including apple, pear, peach and banana trees). Kitchen features granite counters w/large bar, tiled backsplash, farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances. Hardwood floors throughout. Two gas fireplaces (up/down). Two Laundry Rooms (Stackable Unit remains).  $50K Solar Panel System installed! 3 Car attached garage with extended driveway. Newer architectural roof, freshly painted. Too much to list!
